@proposalApi = http://localhost:5001
@contractingApi = http://localhost:5002
@proposalId = replace-with-created-proposal-id
@contractId = replace-with-created-contract-id

### Proposal API health
GET {{proposalApi}}/health

### Contracting API health
GET {{contractingApi}}/health

### Create proposal
# Copy the "id" value from the response into @proposalId.
POST {{proposalApi}}/api/proposals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Maria Silva",
  "insuranceType": "Auto",
  "coverageAmount": 15000
}

### Approve proposal
PATCH {{proposalApi}}/api/proposals/{{proposalId}}/approve

### Create contract
# Copy the "id" value from the response into @contractId.
POST {{contractingApi}}/api/contracts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proposalId": "{{proposalId}}"
}

### Get contract
GET {{contractingApi}}/api/contracts/{{contractId}}
